    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is routed through a Getrag six-speed manual transmission to a variable M Differential Lock. The chassis is mechanically sound, with the rear subframe reinforced and the dual-VANOS system recently overhauled to ensure optimal camshaft timing. While the exterior shows minor road wear, the performance remains sharp with a linear torque curve and crisp throttle response. Riding on staggered alloys with refreshed bushings, this example offers the tactile feedback and mechanical purity enthusiasts demand.",
